S.FORM: nqwaq (ke' na Plmukan: ) ga spiyang balay qbuci hi' hi na kneril ru mlikuy. qutux hi' ga qutux nqwaq ta. cyux maki' te kyahu' nguhuw qu nqwaq na squliq. mhtuw su tanux ga blaq smi sabuw nqwaq. (Te Ciwal qmalan mlahang inbu na Punu)
